data.description: Making a move to the country? This is a great house to begin your journey!!  Small gated community only 20 minutes from downtown and 15 min to major shopping and commerce.  Best of both worlds with no city taxes. 4th bedroom could be used as an office. In the owners have completed the following repairs and upgrades:  New roof 3 years ago with 30 year warranty, New A/C system 8 years ago, New water heater 1 year ago.  Covered 12 X 12 back deck. 1.87 ac of beautiful trees in a quiet, small neighborhood.
